data.description: Interface for ELV WS2500PC weather logger
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
The package Device::WS2000::IO interfaces an older version of this
    interface. However the used protocols are completly different. This
    package is a complete wrapper for all documented functions, so that
    the data can easily be retrieved. Depends on Device::SerialPort,
    Time::HiRes and Time::Local.
